- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to develop the system. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with conversational systems and their ability to incorporate non-task content, which could involve sound-based interactions. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed framework in engaging human users.
